title: Wahoe County educators to rally to stand up for public education 5 hours ago
content: Washoe County School District      Washoe County educators met at the Washoe County Complex at 1001 E. Ninth Street on June 2 to stand up and help students.    The rally will include teachers, administration, students, unions, and community members.    The attendees will stand up for a quality public education for all Nevada students regardless of zip code or income level.     This rally is a way of getting the public to see teachers and the community coming together to vote for the students.
